                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7731" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1212</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1757 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硅谷银行爆雷：连续加息背景下金融风险暴露</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Silicon Valley Bank Went Wrong:Financial Risk Exposure in the Context of Continuous Interest Rate Hikes </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘德红，郭文心，王佳雯，袁江磊，袁沐曦，黄超</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">美国硅谷银行</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硅谷银行；爆雷；连续加息；金融风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Silicon Valley Bank; Went Wrong; Continuous Interest Rate Hikes; Financial Risk</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023年3月10日，美国硅谷银行在经历了210亿美元证券投资组合抛售和储户挤兑后，银行股价单日跌幅超过60%，宣布了破产倒闭，激起了业界的恐慌情绪，金融风险暴露。本案例为了帮助学生深挖事件原因、得出硅谷银行倒闭相关启示建议，特结合美联储连续加息的现实背景，探讨硅谷银行自身长期以来的存贷款配比、业务发展模式和资本投资策略，思考利率变动对于银行经营情况的影响。另外，本案例也通过和学生讲授硅谷银行面临的风险以及联邦存款保险公司等金融机构的应对措施，探讨我国现行金融监管模式，联想至我国对此类金融风险的预防。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On March 10, 2023, after experiencing a $21 billion portfolio sell-off and depositor run, the stock price of Silicon Valley Bank in the United States fell by more than 60% in a single day, announcing bankruptcy and bankruptcy, sparking panic in the industry and exposing financial risks. In order to help students delve deeper into the causes of the event and provide insights and suggestions related to the collapse of Silicon Valley banks, this case explores the long-term deposit loan ratio, business development model, and capital investment strategy of Silicon Valley banks, taking into account the reality of the Federal Reserve&#39;s continuous interest rate hikes, and considers the impact of interest rate changes on bank operations. In addition, this case also explores the current financial regulatory model in China by teaching students about the risks faced by Silicon Valley banks and the countermeasures taken by financial institutions such as the Federal Deposit Insurance Company, and is associated with China&#39;s prevention of such financial risks.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《金融市场与金融机构》、《投资学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">利率结构；债券久期；利率风险；流动性风险；商业银行风险。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
